    "name": "Twin Stick Tennis",
    "steam_appid": 2354060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/b04ee9bb58287961901b3d5103eb74d5.poster.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/b04ee9bb58287961901b3d5103eb74d5.webm?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/b04ee9bb58287961901b3d5103eb74d5.mp4?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome, aspiring ball smacker,</h2>Twin Stick Tennis mixes tennis simulation with wacky arcade tennis. Just like real tennis, this game is about court positioning, shot preparation, and timing smacks. Customize your experience by adjusting the game pace through ball and racket selection.<br><br>Combine these elements you can play slow tactical padel matches or test your reflexes in lightning-fast tennis matches. Victory is at your fingertips as you have full control of the player and racket (see gif above). Celebrate becoming a champion or give your racket a stare of disapproval.<br><br>Have fun smacking balls!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Tennis</h2>Play some epic high pace tennis matches<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/acfa50dfd9d50ce32d14d1a9b0f9a250.poster.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/acfa50dfd9d50ce32d14d1a9b0f9a250.webm?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/acfa50dfd9d50ce32d14d1a9b0f9a250.mp4?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Padel</h2>Smack the ball around the walls to outplay your opponent!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/ee2695943f03a36c2e3527a0e46d65be.poster.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/ee2695943f03a36c2e3527a0e46d65be.webm?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/ee2695943f03a36c2e3527a0e46d65be.mp4?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Shots Featured</h2>Spice up your game with: Topspin, Backspin, Power shots, Drop shots and Lobs. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/f6e2b344b7ef67a2f12115d08c7253d0.poster.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/f6e2b344b7ef67a2f12115d08c7253d0.webm?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/f6e2b344b7ef67a2f12115d08c7253d0.mp4?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Court Surfaces</h2>All major court surfaces included:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/e96d80745a12c58cfd20dd5b0be8a2fb.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Court Sizing</h2>Resize the court to customize your ball smacking experience. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/9f8141ae102b13cfd5b0902e9bc3b3a4.poster.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/9f8141ae102b13cfd5b0902e9bc3b3a4.webm?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/9f8141ae102b13cfd5b0902e9bc3b3a4.mp4?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Train Against the Ball Cannon</h2>Test your reflexes against the brutal ball cannon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/34db1547c678ca703fd517f3877c9c11.poster.avif?t=1709721999\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/34db1547c678ca703fd517f3877c9c11.webm?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354060/extras/34db1547c678ca703fd517f3877c9c11.mp4?t=1709721999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Get good and unlock new balls, rackets and courts<br></li><li> Disable/Enable tennis rules (double hits, wall hits, player hits,  volley on serve and hits on the wrong side of the net)<br></li><li> Local multiplayer mode to compete with your friends<br></li><li> Auto-balancing mode, shrinking racket size for the winning player, growing racket size for the losing player<br></li><li> Diverse CPU play styles<br></li><li> Up to 144 fps supported</li></ul>",
